➜“蔬菜基地就是咱的‘扶贫车间’”
http://www.sohu.com/a/427803728_114731	7951
<p align="center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201028/7ce57b1e4462424b81b96ec63aed2159.jpeg" /></p>
<p align="center"><span>摘黄瓜。</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201028/aac69cd0c005440aba2e6ba9f8911155.jpeg" /></p>
<p align="center"><span>采摘豆角。</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201028/2a6d3bca589a4c5eb76b9ac103734ee8.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
